No. 540, No. 573,

October Term, 1952.

October Term, 1952.

United States v. Nugent; and United States v. Packer,

346 U. S. 1. Petition for rehearing denied. Motions to correct and for clarification of the opinion also denied.

The Chief Justice and Mr. Justice Jackson took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
